flex2.compiler.mxml.lang

Class StandardDefs

  • java.lang.Object
    • flex2.compiler.mxml.lang.StandardDefs
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StandardDefs.StandardDefs2006

    public abstract class StandardDefs
extends Object
    MXML standard (i.e., framework-independent) AS support classes, packages, import sets, etc. NOTE: definition names (interface*, class*) are generally stored here in internal format, usable for typetable lookups. Use NameFormatter.toDot() to convert to source code format. (Note: an exception is lists of import names, in dot format already.) A few select constants are interned, primarily because they are utilized during AST generation.
